title: Vienna In Love
text:
Vienna In Love are a British alternative rock band, formed in London in 2011 by singer-guitarist Victor Cobbs and guitarist Branko Stefanovic. Vienna In Love's influences include  The Cure,  Placebo, Echo & the Bunnymen, Kent, and U2. Their single "Tokyo" was ranked at number 7 on The MTV Adria 's Top 20 DomaÄ‡ica Chart on 2 October 2016.


== Touring ==
Vienna In Love tour in various countries from Europe and the United States, They also performed at various music festivals like  Exit Festival and Arenal Sound
